## ๐ฏ ะขะะฅะะะงะะกะะะ ะะะขะะะ

### Backend
- Python 3.x
- Flask 3.1.2
- Requests 2.32.5
- PID Process Manager
- Graceful Shutdown Handler

### Frontend
- HTML5
- CSS3 (Modern Design)
- Vanilla JavaScript
- Fetch API

### API Integration
- Gate.io API v4
- HMAC-SHA512 Authentication
- REST API
- WebSocket ready

### Security
- PID-based process isolation
- API key storage
- Secure shutdown
- Process validation

